H0.text: Which Italian liqueur is a key ingredient of the well known cocktail, Harvey Wallbanger. Limoncello

H1.text: Which Italian liqueur is a key ingredient of the well known cocktail, Harvey Wallbanger. Sambuca

H2.text: Which Italian liqueur is a key ingredient of the well known cocktail, Harvey Wallbanger. Amaro Nonino

H3.text: Which Italian liqueur is a key ingredient of the well known cocktail, Harvey Wallbanger. Galliano

A4.text: The Harvey Wallbanger is a mixed drink made with vodka, Galliano, and orange juice.

A5.text: The Harvey Wallbanger was created in 1969 as a marketing campaign by McKesson Imports Company, importer of Galliano.
